snippets.title: SecurityCenter bulkMuteFindings Sample
snippets.description: Kicks off an LRO to bulk mute findings for a parent based on a filter. The parent can be either an organization, folder or project. The findings matched by the filter will be muted after the LRO is done.

snippets.description: Creates a source.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter createFinding Sample
snippets.description: Creates a finding. The corresponding source must exist for finding creation to succeed.

snippets.description: Creates a mute config.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter groupAssets Sample
snippets.description: Filters an organization's assets and  groups them by their specified properties.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter groupFindings Sample
snippets.description: Filters an organization or source's findings and  groups them by their specified properties. To group across all sources provide a `-` as the source id. Example: /v1/organizations/{organization_id}/sources/-/findings, /v1/folders/{folder_id}/sources/-/findings, /v1/projects/{project_id}/sources/-/findings

snippets.title: SecurityCenter listAssets Sample
snippets.description: Lists an organization's assets.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter listFindings Sample
snippets.description: Lists an organization or source's findings. To list across all sources provide a `-` as the source id. Example: /v1/organizations/{organization_id}/sources/-/findings

snippets.title: SecurityCenter listMuteConfigs Sample
snippets.description: Lists mute configs.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter listNotificationConfigs Sample
snippets.description: Lists notification configs.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter listSources Sample
snippets.description: Lists all sources belonging to an organization.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter runAssetDiscovery Sample
snippets.description: Runs asset discovery. The discovery is tracked with a long-running operation. This API can only be called with limited frequency for an organization. If it is called too frequently the caller will receive a TOO_MANY_REQUESTS error.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter setFindingState Sample
snippets.description: Updates the state of a finding.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter setMute Sample
snippets.description: Updates the mute state of a finding.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter setIamPolicy Sample
snippets.description: Sets the access control policy on the specified Source.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter testIamPermissions Sample
snippets.description: Returns the permissions that a caller has on the specified source.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter updateExternalSystem Sample
snippets.description: Updates external system. This is for a given finding.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter updateFinding Sample
snippets.description: Creates or updates a finding. The corresponding source must exist for a finding creation to succeed.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter updateNotificationConfig Sample
snippets.description: Updates a notification config. The following update fields are allowed: description, pubsub_topic, streaming_config.filter

snippets.title: SecurityCenter updateOrganizationSettings Sample
snippets.description: Updates an organization's settings.

snippets.description: Deletes an existing big query export.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter updateBigQueryExport Sample
snippets.description: Updates a BigQuery export.

snippets.title: SecurityCenter listBigQueryExports Sample
snippets.description: Lists BigQuery exports. Note that when requesting BigQuery exports at a given level all exports under that level are also returned e.g. if requesting BigQuery exports under a folder, then all BigQuery exports immediately under the folder plus the ones created under the projects within the folder are returned.
